<section class="join-area ptb-100 ">
<div class="container">
<div class="row">
<div class="col-lg-6 col-md-6">
<div class="join-content">
<h3>Try our tax service you will get the result you want.</h3>

<p>We are No 1 in Australia in preparing Police Members tax returns. Join the other 3,500 Police officers who use our tax preparation service Australia wide.</p>

<ul class="accordion">
	<li class="accordion-item"><a class="accordion-title active" href="javascript:void(0)">How long have you been preparing Police Tax for?</a>

	<p class="accordion-content show">We have been preparing Tax returns for law enforcement officers for the last 30 year so you can be sure we understand your job and how important it is to get the highest legal refund without the hassles of accountants not understanding your work role.</p>
